SHERATON-CARLTON
HOTEL
WASHINGTON, D.C.

THE TOBACCO INSTITUTE
FIFTH ANNUAL 
COLLEGE OF TOBACCO KNOWLEDGE
FEBRUARY 19-21, 1980
REGISTRATION FORM

NAME: GEORGE R. TELFORD
TITLE: Brand Manager
COMPANY: Lorillard
ADDRESS: 666 Fifth Avenue, New York, NY 10019
PHONE: (212) 841-8787

CHECK ONE:
___ Please reserve a room for me at the Sheraton-Carlton.
_x_ I will make my own housing arrangements.

ARRIVAL DATE AND TIME: 2/18/80 7:00 P.M.
DEPARTURE DATE AND TIME: 2/21/80 4:00 P.M.

Please attach a brief (50 words or so) autobiographical sketch.
Note your first name or nickname, your current professional responsibilities,
employment background and whatever personal information you feel would be helpful in giving your fellow students an idea of your activities and interests. The sketches will be assembled and provided at the opening class session.

Any questions? Call Connie Drath or Carol Musgrave at 800/424-9876.

**PLEASE RETURN IN SELF-ADDRESSED ENVELOPE BY FRIDAY, JANUARY 18, 1980**
